tyling. I'm ensuring an intuitive and clear selection mechanism.\n\n\n**Styling Button Attributes**\n\nI'm now refining the entity selector's visual style, focusing on button attributes. I'm leveraging Tailwind classes to establish distinct states: base, hover, and active. I'm focusing on text and background colors and hover effects for enhanced user interaction. The objective is intuitive visual feedback. The layout is progressing well.\n\n\n**Developing Table Headings**\n\nI'm now generating table headings, utilizing consistent styling for readability. I'm focusing on attributes, types, and descriptions, employing font choices and color to enhance presentation.\n\n\n**Implementing Key Visuals**\n\nI'm now integrating primary and sort key displays. I'm leveraging distinct colors and styling to highlight the key data within the table representation. I'm focusing on text size and background nuances to enhance readability and ensure the key attributes stand out effectively. This is coming together well.\n\n\n**Highlighting Attribute Details**\n\nI'm now integrating detailed attribute information within the table representation. I'm leveraging distinct styling for enhanced readability of the attribute name, type, and description. I'm focusing on concise visual elements, using contrasting colors and font treatments for an engaging presentation.\n\n\n**Refining Index Sort Keys**\n\nI'm now integrating the visual display for index sort keys, specifically within the table representation. I'm focusing on concise presentation within the table, ensuring clarity and readability. I'm refining the styling to visually distinguish the index sort keys. I'm ensuring all the styling is clear and consistent.\n\n\n**Integrating JSON Visuals**\n\nI'm now integrating a sample JSON payload display, focusing on visual clarity. I'm dynamically fetching the JSON based on user selections and presenting it within a dedicated block. I'm working to ensure it's easy to read and complements the table data effectively, considering various JSON structures. I've focused on styling to make sure the structure is clear.\n\n\n**Adding Copy to Clipboard**\n\nI've just added a \"Copy Payload\" button. Clicking this copies the sample JSON to the clipboard. The button styling complements the overall look. I'm focusing on user-friendly interactivity to enhance the experience.\n\n\n"}}
