x Troubleshooting to Section 5). The panel features high-contrast visual selectors, colored PK/SK row identifiers, structured schema property attributes tables, and interactive JSON payload displays with single-click copy mechanisms.\n   - Fixed the \"Decoupled Local DB\" prod paradigm value in Sandbox boundaries grid to accurately denote Amazon DynamoDB Single-Table Design.\n\n3. **Validation & Code Quality**:\n   - Verified that both TypeScript compilation (`npx tsc --noEmit`) and ESLint validation (`npm run lint`) pass with 100% compliance and zero warnings or errors.\n   - Confirmed mobile responsiveness and responsive scaling across grids, layout containers, horizontal scrolls, and overflow tables.\n   - Handled all interactions safely, keeping standard sandbox mocking mechanisms intact. No landing page files were altered, nor were any dynamic slug pages or route bypasses introduced.","verified":true}}}
